headline.main: GAYDA SEEKS LIGHT ON LONG'S ADDRESS; He Intimates Some of Material Was Obtained From Phillips

lead_paragraph: ROME, Oct. 22 -- A diplomatic incident between Italy and the United States was intimated by Virginio Gayda today, who discussed the possibility that William Phillips, United States Ambassador to Italy, had something to do with Breckenridge Long's speech at Detroit on Oct. 19.
